inputs.lyrics:
[inst]

[verse]
In the shadows where secrets hide,
We're bound by chains, inside we slide.
With promises they blind our eyes,
Yet we rise, to challenge lies.

[chorus]
We're the rebels, with fire in our hearts,
Against the chains, breaking apart.
No surrender, no retreat,
Together we fight, a new world meet.

[verse]
Through the whispers of power's might,
They try to silence, but our spirits light.
In the silence, our voices hear,
Uniting now, our destiny clear.

[chorus]
We're the rebels, with fire in our hearts,
Against the chains, breaking apart.
No surrender, no retreat,
Together we fight, a new world meet.

[bridge]
From the depths of fear to the heights of dreams,
We stand against their endless schemes.
With every beat, our spirits scream,
Freedom's call, our future gleam.

[chorus]
We're the rebels, with fire in our hearts,
Against the chains, breaking apart.
No surrender, no retreat,
Together we fight, a new world meet.

[verse]
Through the echoes of time so bold,
Stories of freedom, strong and old.
With every step, we reclaim,
The truth untold, we proclaim.

[chorus]
We're the rebels, with fire in our hearts,
Against the chains, breaking apart.
No surrender, no retreat,
Together we fight, a new world meet.

[Outro]
In this anthem, our spirits soar,
Bound by courage, forevermore.
Rebel hearts, together beat,
Breaking free from their defeat.
